<br>
Now on epics. I take tremendous pride in wielding Swiftwind and Earthcaller. There may be better weapons out there now but I will always be very proud on having achieved these weapons. It took the work of myself and many friends inorder for me to wield these swords and that experience far outways whether there are better available. <br>
