<br>
The effect Swift Spirit not only gives you 40% item haste but also adds about 30 or 40 to your attack rating (I forget the exact number atm).  The increased attack will increase your DPS with whatever weapon you hold in your main hand and with your bow.  <br>
<br>
This is the main reason most rangers never give up Swiftwind.<br>
<br>
Earthcaller gets bagged more often because of the aggro drawing, mezz breaking proc and because you can find things with better DPS on them.  Not to mention Earthcaller is the more difficult of the two blades to get. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#1F0000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=deeceyriverwind>DeeceyRiverwind</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Qeynos Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#AAAAAA>(11/25/02 5:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=50.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Lauri</span><hr size=1> Lauri, you can contact me under FuttererJ@t-online.de <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#0E0E0E><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pricecheckgirl>PriceCheckGirl</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lonely in Kera Ridge</span><br>  Posts: 184<br> <font color=#AAAAAA>(11/25/02 6:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=50.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   you got mail</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
